'''德魯大學'''（Drew University）是位於美國[[新澤西州|新澤西州]][[麥迪遜_(新澤西州)|麥迪遜]]的一所[[私立大學|私立大學]]，因爲校區位于{{convert|186|acre}}的森林中而得到暱稱“森林大學”（University in the Forest） 。該大學創立于1867年，本是美國商人[[丹尼爾·德魯|丹尼爾·德魯]]為衛理公會成立的神學院，1928年擴大成爲[[文理學院|文理學院]]，1955年開始接受研究生入學。其本科生學費在2015-2016學年間達59,661美元，使其成爲新澤西州内學費最貴的大學。<ref name="TuitionCosts">Drew University. [http://www.drew.edu/financialassistance/tuition-and-fees "Cost of Attendance and Overview of Aid"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.drew.edu/financialassistance/tuition-and-fees |date=20170320035227 }}. Retrieved 15 October 2013.</ref> 該學院在2015年《[[美國新聞與世界報道|美國新聞與世界報道]]》的全美文理學院排名中列在第112位。<ref name="USnews">{{cite web|title=Drew University|url=http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/drew-university-2603|publisher=[[美國新聞與世界報道|美國新聞與世界報道]]|accessdate=2015-11-26|archive-date=2015-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905104515/http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/drew-university-2603|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 校區==
[[File:Mead_Hall_Drew_U_jeh.jpg|thumb]]
該大學位於美國[[新澤西州|新澤西州]][[麥迪遜_(新澤西州)|麥迪遜]]，東距[[紐約市|紐約市]]25英里<ref name="NYTProfileMadisonNJ">Caldwell, Dave. [https://www.nytimes.com/2008/06/15/realestate/15livi.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0 "Living in Madison, N.J.; A Town Right Out of Central Casting"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2008/06/15/realestate/15livi.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0 |date=20210101074110 }} in ''The New York Times'' (15 June 2008). Retrieved 13 October 2013.</ref>。大學校區用地和部分建築原屬經營船隻業務的商人威廉·吉布森（William Gibbons，1794–1852），他在1832年買下了麥迪遜{{convert|95|acres}}的土地<ref>New Jersey Historical Society. [http://www.jerseyhistory.org/findingaid.php?aid=1302 Manuscript Group 1302, Gibbons Family (Savannah, GA and Madison, NJ)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.jerseyhistory.org/findingaid.php?aid=1302 |date=20140902163843 }}. Retrieved 13 October 2013.</ref><ref>Esposito, Frank J. ''The Madison Heritage Trail: An Intimate History of a Community in Transition'' (The Madison Bicentennial Heritage Committee: Madison, New Jersey, 1985), 61-62, 83-84.</ref>。次年他開始此建造一座[[希臘復興式建築|希臘復興式建築]]，用作自宅。該建築在1936年完工，即Gibbons Mansion。1867年鐵路大亨[[丹尼爾·德魯|丹尼爾·德魯]]從吉布森的後人手中以14萬美元的價格買下這塊地方<ref name="MeadHallHistory">Drew University. [http://www.drew.edu/fomh/history "A Brief History of Mead Hall"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131024133534/http://www.drew.edu/fomh/history |date=2013-10-24 }}. Retrieved 13 October 2013.</ref><ref name="CunninghamImagesMadison">Cunningham, John T. ''Images of America: Madison'' (Dover, New Hampshire: Arcadia Publishing, 1998), 19, 31.</ref>，然後將其捐給了衛理公會<ref name="MeadHallHistory" /><ref name="CunninghamImagesMadison" />，吉布森的住宅也依德魯之妻羅莎娜·米德（Roxanna Mead）之名改爲Mead Hall<ref name="MeadHallHistory" />。

後來德魯大學建造的建築主要為希臘復興式、哥特復興式和新古典主義式。所處的森林則是一個保護區，由該大學和[[輝瑞公司|輝瑞公司]]、[[美國魚類及野生動物保護局|美國魚類及野生動物保護局]]維護<ref name="DrewPreserveAudubon">Parke, John. [http://www.njaudubon.org/SectionConservation/StewardshipProgam/StewardshipBlog/tabid/2006/entryid/38/Reforestation-and-a-Partnership-Grows-at-Drew-University.aspx Stewardship Blog: "Reforestation and a Partnership Grows at Drew University"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.njaudubon.org/SectionConservation/StewardshipProgam/StewardshipBlog/tabid/2006/entryid/38/Reforestation-and-a-Partnership-Grows-at-Drew-University.aspx |date=20150104202757 }}, New Jersey Audubon Society (10 June 2011). Retrieved 13 October 2013.</ref>。森林裡還有两個池塘，生活着各種魚類和水鳥<ref name="DrewPreserveAudubon" /><ref>Drew University. [https://uknow.drew.edu/confluence/display/DrewHistory/Zuck+Arboretum Buildings & Campus Locations: Zuck Arboretum] {{Wayback|url=https://uknow.drew.edu/confluence/display/DrewHistory/Zuck+Arboretum |date=20210101074154 }}. Retrieved 13 October 2013.</ref>。

